  text: Use a reverse loop so column positions don’t shift while deleting.

**VBA solution:**
```vb
Sub DeleteDescriptionColumns()
    Dim ws As Worksheet
    Dim c As Long
    
    Set ws = ActiveSheet
    
    For c = ws.Cells(1, ws.Columns.Count).End(xlToLeft).Column To 1 Step -1
        If InStr(1, ws.Cells(1, c).Value, "/description", vbTextCompare) > 0 Then
            ws.Columns(c).Delete
        End If
    Next c
End Sub
```

